com.google.enterprise.connector.spi

Class DocumentNotFoundException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.RepositoryException
          • com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.RepositoryDocumentException
            • com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.DocumentNotFoundException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DocumentNotFoundException
extends RepositoryDocumentException
    Thrown for documents that do not exist or are unknown to the connector.

    It is the responsibility of the Connector to construct a checkpoint that skips over the offending Document if DocumentList.checkpoint() is called after DocumentNotFoundException is thrown.

    Since:
    3.0
